ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAdvisory Council on the Implementation of National Pharmacare
PrecisOrder establishing the Advisory Council on the IMPLENTATION OF NATIONAL PHARMACARE in order to provide independent advice to the Minister of Health and the Minister of Finance on how to best implement national pharmacare in a manner that is affordable for Canadians and their families, employers and governments.
